Providing reliable and surreptitious communications is difficult in the presence of adaptive and resourceful state level censors. When compared to state-of-the-art Bitcoin writing solutions, Tithonus reduces the cost of transferring data to censored clients by 2 orders of magnitude and increases the goodput by 3 to 5 orders of magnitude
