Here, we demonstrate an intra-chip MDM communications link employing advanced modulation formats with two waveguide modes. Each of the mode channels achieves 100 Gb/s line rate with 84 Gb/s net payload data rate at 7% overhead for hard-decision forward error correction (HD-FEC) in the OFDM/16-QAM signal transmission.
Link: https://arxiv.org/abs/1702.03216
